      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel? This car is in poor condition and will definitely need some mechanical and cosmetic TLC, but it's an incredible opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a great value! With a bit of work and dedication, you can bring this vehicle back to life and make it your own. It's priced to sell and ready for its next chapter with a handy new owner!",
