    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable choice for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While it runs well and has been maintained mechanically, the exterior shows expected wear for its age, including some minor door dings, surface scratches, and slight paint fading on the hood. The interior is clean but shows some thinning in the upholstery and minor wear on the control buttons. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for the road.",
