      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the paint on the hood, and a few small dings along the door panels. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. While the car starts and runs, it will likely need some mechanical attention soon, such as new tires and a brake service, to ensure long-term reliability. It serves as a solid, functional transportation option for someone willing to put in a little bit of maintenance work.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard. It offers a seamless integration of performance and reliability, characterized by a well-preserved aesthetic and a robust mechanical profile. This offering represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a high-caliber experience and enduring value.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
